pref-usage-title = Quick usage
pref-usage-step1 = Load the unpacked extension from the chrome-extension folder in chrome://extensions.
pref-usage-step2 = Log into ChatGPT, Gemini, or your custom site in your normal Chrome profile.
pref-usage-step3 = Select a paper or open its PDF reader in Zotero, then trigger “Ask in Web AI”.
pref-usage-step4 = Review the populated message in Chrome and click Send manually.
pref-extension-note = The extension reads a one-time task payload from the opened page and then clears that payload from the URL immediately.
